    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# e001-01-wavelets-baseline\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**ResNet GAN baseline z hinge loss, SpectralNorm, EMA, DiffAugment**\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Opis eksperymentu\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Dataset**: CelebA 128×128 (faces)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Architektura**: ResNet GAN\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Loss**: Hinge loss\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Regularizacja**: SpectralNorm w D, DiffAugment (color, translation, cutout)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **EMA**: decay 0.999\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Optimizer**: Adam (lr=2e-4, betas=(0.0, 0.99))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Profile\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `preview` - 200 kroków, live gridy, \\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `smoke` - 500 kroków, szybki test\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- `train` - 30k kroków, pełny trening z FID/KID\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## Metryki\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Co iter: loss_D, loss_G, grad_norm_D/G, sec/iter, VRAM peak\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Co 1k: sample grid\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Co 5k: checkpoint\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Co 10k: FID/KID\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
